gamerule.doWardenBlindness.description: Controls whether or not Wardens apply the Blindness effect to nearby players. This is a temporary fix while this mod's developer figures out how to stop shader packs from disabling the Darkness Effect.
gamerule.doWardenDarkness.description: Controls whether or not Wardens apply the Darkness effect to nearby players.
